I call it your
physical intelligence.

00:17:42.150 --> 00:17:44.080 align:middle line:84%
>>LISA: Yes, my
stomach turns to stone.

00:17:44.080 --> 00:17:44.790 align:middle line:90%
>>SANGWAN: Right.

00:17:44.790 --> 00:17:46.373 align:middle line:84%
Well, that's an
uncomfortable feeling.

00:17:46.373 --> 00:17:49.620 align:middle line:84%
So most people will go
first and numb that out.

00:17:49.620 --> 00:17:50.120 align:middle line:90%
>>LISA: OK.

00:17:50.120 --> 00:17:52.007 align:middle line:90%
>>SANGWAN: So-- excuse me.

00:17:52.007 --> 00:17:54.090 align:middle line:84%
What they'll do is they'll
