>>LISA: Yeah.

00:17:55.780 --> 00:17:56.500 align:middle line:90%
>>SANGWAN: OK?

00:17:56.500 --> 00:17:58.470 align:middle line:84%
So the first step is
actually tuning in.

00:17:58.470 --> 00:17:59.046 align:middle line:90%
>>LISA: OK.

00:17:59.046 --> 00:18:01.420 align:middle line:84%
>>SANGWAN: And when you do,
there's a lot of ways to tune

00:18:01.420 --> 00:18:01.920 align:middle line:90%
in.

00:18:01.920 --> 00:18:05.360 align:middle line:84%
Some people take deep breaths,
they manage themselves.

00:18:05.360 --> 00:18:08.620 align:middle line:84%
It's that discomfort
in someone's body

00:18:08.620 --> 00:18:10.970 align:middle line:84%
that stops them from
speaking their truth.

00:18:10.970 --> 00:18:12.090 align:middle line:90%
But this is the secret.

00:18:12.090 --> 00:18:13.000 align:middle line:90%
>>LISA: OK.

00:18:13.000 --> 00:18:15.260 align:middle line:84%
>>SANGWAN: The secret is
you come to a decision point

00:18:15.260 --> 00:18:16.320 align:middle line:90%
many times in your day.

00:18:16.320 --> 00:18:18.040 align:middle line:90%
Do I tell the truth, do I not?

00:18:18.040 --> 00:18:20.227 align:middle line:84%
Do I say what I really
mean, do I hold back?

00:18:20.227 --> 00:18:20.810 align:middle line:90%
>>LISA: Right.

00:18:20.810 --> 00:18:21.000 align:middle line:90%
>>SANGWAN: Right?

00:18:21.000 --> 00:18:21.900 align:middle line:90%
>>LISA: Right.

00:18:21.900 --> 00:18:26.890 align:middle line:84%
>>SANGWAN: The deal is that
if you feel that discomfort

00:18:26.890 --> 00:18:31.170 align:middle line:84%
and you numb it, you're going to
get a short term effect, which

00:18:31.170 --> 00:18:33.080 align:middle line:84%
is your short term high
of just avoiding it.

00:18:33.080 --> 00:18:34.350 align:middle line:90%
Like, ooh, got away with that.

00:18:34.350 --> 00:18:34.780 align:middle line:90%
>>LISA: Right.

00:18:34.780 --> 00:18:35.280 align:middle line:90%
Right.

00:18:35.280 --> 00:18:36.571 align:middle line:90%
I escaped the lion.

00:18:36.571 --> 00:18:37.070 align:middle line:90%
Right.

00:18:37.070 --> 00:18:37.340 align:middle line:90%
>>SANGWAN: Right?

00:18:37.340 --> 00:18:37.840 align:middle line:90%
Oh, ooh.

00:18:37.840 --> 00:18:39.710 align:middle line:84%
Thank God I escaped
that conflict.

00:18:39.710 --> 00:18:43.590 align:middle line:84%
But long term, every time
you look in the mirror,

00:18:43.590 --> 00:18:46.620 align:middle line:84%
you're going to respect
yourself a little bit less.

00:18:46.620 --> 00:18:48.060 align:middle line:84%
Wow, why didn't I
have the courage

00:18:48.060 --> 00:18:49.320 align:middle line:90%
to stand up and say that?

00:18:49.320 --> 00:18:52.130 align:middle line:84%
How come I didn't say what I
really meant in that meeting?

00:18:52.130 --> 00:18:55.320 align:middle line:84%
How come I didn't tell them
that that wasn't OK, right?

00:18:55.320 --> 00:18:58.460 align:middle line:84%
Now the flip side of that is
you come to that decision point

00:18:58.460 --> 00:19:00.850 align:middle line:84%
and you become aware of
the physical intelligence

00:19:00.850 --> 00:19:01.730 align:middle line:90%
in your body.

00:19:01.730 --> 00:19:03.287 align:middle line:90%
And you decide, you know what?

00:19:03.287 --> 00:19:05.620 align:middle line:84%
I'm going to use my breathing,
I'm going to calm myself,

00:19:05.620 --> 00:19:08.130 align:middle line:84%
and I'm going to deal with
the short term discomfort--

00:19:08.130 --> 00:19:11.530 align:middle line:84%
not the short term high of
avoiding it or numbing it.

00:19:11.530 --> 00:19:13.920 align:middle line:84%
You're going to take the
short term discomfort

00:19:13.920 --> 00:19:17.490 align:middle line:84%
and lean into that
discomfort for the long term

00:19:17.490 --> 00:19:22.380 align:middle line:84%
high of liking yourself, of
having great relationships,

00:19:22.380 --> 00:19:23.860 align:middle line:90%
of investing in your life.

00:19:23.860 --> 00:19:25.250 align:middle line:84%
So one thing I
don't say is, this

00:19:25.250 --> 00:19:26.800 align:middle line:90%
is going to ever become easy.

00:19:26.800 --> 00:19:28.330 align:middle line:90%
It's not even easy for me.

00:19:28.330 --> 00:19:29.707 align:middle line:90%
>>LISA: So you said lean into--

00:19:29.707 --> 00:19:30.790 align:middle line:90%
>>SANGWAN: The discomfort.

00:19:30.790 --> 00:19:32.720 align:middle line:90%
It's only short term.

00:19:32.720 --> 00:19:36.210 align:middle line:84%
Because the thing that gets
these signals to go away

00:19:36.210 --> 00:19:38.310 align:middle line:84%
is that you actually
acknowledge and address them.

00:19:38.310 --> 00:19:39.810 align:middle line:84%
>>LISA: That you say
something about it.

00:19:39.810 --> 00:19:40.200 align:middle line:90%
>>SANGWAN: Yes.

00:19:40.200 --> 00:19:40.740 align:middle line:90%
>>LISA: Absolutely.

00:19:40.740 --> 00:19:42.281 align:middle line:84%
>>SANGWAN: So that's
the first thing.

00:19:42.281 --> 00:19:44.580 align:middle line:84%
The first thing is, you've
got to know your signals.

00:19:44.580 --> 00:19:45.540 align:middle line:84%
You've got to know
that there is going

00:19:45.540 --> 00:19:46.570 align:middle line:90%
to be a little discomfort.

00:19:46.570 --> 00:19:48.080 align:middle line:84%
And that's just your
body talking to you.

00:19:48.080 --> 00:19:48.772 align:middle line:90%
>>LISA: Mm hmm.

00:19:48.772 --> 00:19:52.170 align:middle line:84%
And then lean into it and
then override the wave,

00:19:52.170 --> 00:19:53.040 align:middle line:90%
or ride the wave--

00:19:53.040 --> 00:19:53.670 align:middle line:90%
>>SANGWAN: Ride the wave.

00:19:53.670 --> 00:19:55.000 align:middle line:84%
>>LISA: --so that you
can have the greater

00:19:55.000 --> 00:19:56.530 align:middle line:90%
gain, which is that freedom.

00:19:56.530 --> 00:19:57.005 align:middle line:84%
>>SANGWAN: But it's
going to actually

00:19:57.005 --> 00:19:58.061 align:middle line:90%
be a dip of discomfort.

00:19:58.061 --> 00:20:00.060 align:middle line:84%
So it's not going to feel
like riding that wave.

00:20:00.060 --> 00:20:02.270 align:middle line:84%
It's actually going to feel like
when you're on a roller coaster

00:20:02.270 --> 00:20:03.490 align:middle line:90%
and you're just going over.

00:20:03.490 --> 00:20:06.270 align:middle line:84%
Like, oh, this doesn't
feel comfortable.

00:20:06.270 --> 00:20:08.040 align:middle line:84%
Then the second
thing you want to do

00:20:08.040 --> 00:20:11.570 align:middle line:84%
is when you're talking--
let's say it's your boss, OK?

00:20:11.570 --> 00:20:13.850 align:middle line:84%
What you want to say-- or,
let's say you're my boss

00:20:13.850 --> 00:20:15.500 align:middle line:84%
and I need to have
this conversation.

00:20:15.500 --> 00:20:16.000 align:middle line:90%
>>LISA: OK.

00:20:16.000 --> 00:20:16.520 align:middle line:90%
>>SANGWAN: How about that?

00:20:16.520 --> 00:20:16.840 align:middle line:90%
>>LISA: OK.

