Do you see how all
of a sudden, aren't

00:20:24.310 --> 00:20:25.842 align:middle line:84%
some walls going
to go up for you?

00:20:25.842 --> 00:20:26.550 align:middle line:90%
>>LISA: Oh, yeah.

00:20:26.550 --> 00:20:26.820 align:middle line:90%
>>SANGWAN: OK.

