00:36:45.760 --> 00:36:48.780 align:middle line:10%
understood by using an example.

00:36:48.780 --> 00:36:50.620 align:middle line:84%
So let's look at
two interpretations

00:36:50.620 --> 00:36:53.170 align:middle line:90%
of the same scenario.

00:36:53.170 --> 00:36:56.920 align:middle line:84%
