of your performance review

00:36:56.920 --> 00:37:00.780 align:middle line:84%
and you walk by your
boss's office, say hello.

00:37:00.780 --> 00:37:03.760 align:middle line:84%
Your boss looks
up, says nothing,

00:37:03.760 --> 00:37:06.690 align:middle line:84%
and then looks down
and continues texting.

00:37:06.690 --> 00:37:10.950 align:middle line:84%
There are multiple ways that you
can interpret this interaction.

00:37:10.950 --> 00:37:15.310 align:middle line:84%
The first aspect is interpreting
your body's signals.

00:37:15.310 --> 00:37:20.030 align:middle line:84%
They come in both
externally and internally.

00:37:20.030 --> 00:37:25.230 align:middle line:84%
Externally, your body gathers
data through your five senses.

00:37:25.230 --> 00:37:30.130 align:middle line:84%
What you see, hear,
taste, touch, and smell.

00:37:30.130 --> 00:37:32.970 align:middle line:84%
In this scenario, you saw
your boss in his office.

00:37:32.970 --> 00:37:34.800 align:middle line:90%
You said hello.

00:37:34.800 --> 00:37:36.320 align:middle line:90%
You saw him look up at you.

00:37:36.320 --> 00:37:40.190 align:middle line:84%
You heard nothing, and you
saw him resume texting.

00:37:40.190 --> 00:37:43.490 align:middle line:84%
So the senses used to
gather data in this scenario

00:37:43.490 --> 00:37:46.580 align:middle line:84%
would have been your
sight and your hearing.

00:37:46.580 --> 00:37:51.040 align:middle line:84%
So your body also communicates
with you internally.

00:37:51.040 --> 00:37:53.310 align:middle line:84%
It sends you
messages and signals.

00:37:53.310 --> 00:37:56.170 align:middle line:84%
For example, when your
boss didn't answer you,

00:37:56.170 --> 00:38:00.640 align:middle line:84%
your heart may have started
racing or your stomach turning.

00:38:00.640 --> 00:38:02.900 align:middle line:84%
These are also
indications from your body

00:38:02.900 --> 00:38:05.910 align:middle line:84%
that you need to
pay attention to.

00:38:05.910 --> 00:38:07.560 align:middle line:84%
As you interpret
your body's data,

00:38:07.560 --> 00:38:09.400 align:middle line:84%
you then move into
the second part

00:38:09.400 --> 00:38:12.810 align:middle line:84%
of the i-Five conversation,
your thoughts.

00:38:12.810 --> 00:38:14.880 align:middle line:84%
From what you're
just experienced

00:38:14.880 --> 00:38:17.090 align:middle line:84%
you gather this data
