00:38:24.800 --> 00:38:27.010 align:middle line:90%
as well as you did last year.

00:38:27.010 --> 00:38:29.890 align:middle line:84%
So the story you
make up will lead

00:38:29.890 --> 00:38:32.470 align:middle line:84%
to how you feel,
and feelings are

00:38:32.470 --> 00:38:35.990 align:middle line:84%
the third component of
the i-Five conversation.

00:38:35.990 --> 00:38:38.080 align:middle line:84%
In this scenario,
you would likely

00:38:38.080 --> 00:38:41.130 align:middle line:84%
be feeling disappointment,
worry, or fear

00:38:41.130 --> 00:38:43.050 align:middle line:90%
about your upcoming review.

00:38:43.050 --> 00:38:44.840 align:middle line:84%
So this leads us to
the fourth component

00:38:44.840 --> 00:38:48.610 align:middle line:84%
of the i-Five conversation,
interpreting your desires.

00:38:48.610 --> 00:38:52.790 align:middle line:84%
So from this last experience if
you felt disappointment, worry,

00:38:52.790 --> 00:38:55.540 align:middle line:84%
or fear about your
upcoming review,

00:38:55.540 --> 00:38:58.230 align:middle line:84%
this may lead you to want
to talk to your coworkers

00:38:58.230 --> 00:39:00.880 align:middle line:84%
and tell them that your
boss is in a bad mood

00:39:00.880 --> 00:39:03.870 align:middle line:90%
and to avoid him at all costs.

00:39:03.870 --> 00:39:08.800 align:middle line:84%
It may even cause you to want
to avoid your review altogether.

00:39:08.800 --> 00:39:11.660 align:middle line:10%
The final component of
the i-Five conversation

00:39:11.660 --> 00:39:13.680 align:middle line:10%
is integrating all
the other components

00:39:13.680 --> 00:39:15.940 align:middle line:10%
