by being open, curious,

00:40:40.360 --> 00:40:42.040 align:middle line:10%
and receptive.

00:40:42.040 --> 00:40:45.530 align:middle line:10%
From this example, you can
see how the same scenario can

00:40:45.530 --> 00:40:48.740 align:middle line:10%
create dramatically
different outcomes based

00:40:48.740 --> 00:40:52.480 align:middle line:10%
on the story you make up and
how you interpret the five

00:40:52.480 --> 00:40:55.800 align:middle line:10%
components of the
i-Five conversation.

