00:42:39.738 --> 00:42:40.940 align:middle line:90%
>>SANGWAN: OK.

00:42:40.940 --> 00:42:43.094 align:middle line:90%
How old were you?

00:42:43.094 --> 00:42:44.260 align:middle line:90%
>>LISA: This was growing up.

00:42:44.260 --> 00:42:46.450 align:middle line:84%
>>SANGWAN: The first
time you remember it.

00:42:46.450 --> 00:42:47.270 align:middle line:90%
>>LISA: Eight.

00:42:47.270 --> 00:42:47.975 align:middle line:90%
>>SANGWAN: OK.

00:42:47.975 --> 00:42:48.320 align:middle line:90%
>>LISA: Yeah.

00:42:48.320 --> 00:42:48.520 align:middle line:90%
Eight.

00:42:48.520 --> 00:42:49.645 align:middle line:90%
>>SANGWAN: So what happens?

00:42:49.645 --> 00:42:52.050 align:middle line:84%
How do you know that
your husband is actually

00:42:52.050 --> 00:42:54.069 align:middle line:84%
