00:46:41.350 --> 00:46:42.330 align:middle line:90%
>>SANGWAN: Absolutely.

00:46:42.330 --> 00:46:43.000 align:middle line:90%
>>LISA: Talk about that.

00:46:43.000 --> 00:46:44.010 align:middle line:90%
>>SANGWAN: Absolutely.

00:46:44.010 --> 00:46:48.540 align:middle line:84%
So I have clients that
have felt-- I really

00:46:48.540 --> 00:46:51.712 align:middle line:84%
believe at the core, we may
look different externally.

00:46:51.712 --> 00:46:52.920 align:middle line:90%
We may be different cultures.

00:46:52.920 --> 00:46:54.420 align:middle line:84%
We may have been
raised differently.

00:46:54.420 --> 00:46:56.650 align:middle line:84%
But at our core, my
belief is that all of us

00:46:56.650 --> 00:46:59.770 align:middle line:84%
want to be heard,
seen, and valued.

00:46:59.770 --> 00:47:02.200 align:middle line:90%
>>LISA: That is absolutely true.

00:47:02.200 --> 00:47:08.920 align:middle line:84%
>>SANGWAN: And so whether or
not someone feels those things,

00:47:08.920 --> 00:47:13.090 align:middle line:84%
for me I've seen a pretty
strong link to many signals,

00:47:13.090 --> 00:47:16.040 align:middle line:90%
but headaches is a big one.

00:47:16.040 --> 00:47:18.680 align:middle line:84%
And often sometimes
clients who even

00:47:18.680 --> 00:47:23.510 align:middle line:84%
have medical doctors
in their family,

00:47:23.510 --> 00:47:27.920 align:middle line:84%
the only way that they can get
a timeout or a break in the end

00:47:27.920 --> 00:47:31.340 align:middle line:90%
is when they're ill.

00:47:31.340 --> 00:47:34.090 align:middle line:84%
So the way that I can
get you off my back

00:47:34.090 --> 00:47:35.752 align:middle line:84%
is-- and they don't
do it consciously.

00:47:35.752 --> 00:47:36.960 align:middle line:90%
They're not even aware of it.

00:47:36.960 --> 00:47:39.480 align:middle line:84%
They're not even
aware of the link.

00:47:39.480 --> 00:47:43.610 align:middle line:84%
But the way that I can do
that is by, when I am ill,

00:47:43.610 --> 00:47:45.700 align:middle line:84%
I get attention, love,
and care from you,

00:47:45.700 --> 00:47:47.320 align:middle line:84%
because you understand
that language.

00:47:47.320 --> 00:47:49.320 align:middle line:84%
>>LISA: Or I get an excuse
to take a break from you.

00:47:49.320 --> 00:47:50.944 align:middle line:84%
>>SANGWAN: Yeah, and
I get to be quiet.

00:47:50.944 --> 00:47:51.510 align:middle line:90%
I get peace.

00:47:51.510 --> 00:47:53.260 align:middle line:90%
I get space around me.

00:47:53.260 --> 00:47:55.970 align:middle line:84%
So aside from the
people, the other piece

00:47:55.970 --> 00:47:58.480 align:middle line:84%
is when people don't have a
medical community around them,

00:47:58.480 --> 00:48:01.680 align:middle line:84%
